  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of a new exercise machine designed to improve strength and speed of movement in
      the leg muscles. Investigators are trying to learn whether a new training method results in
      greater strength improvements as compared to a traditional method.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
